      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a good start for the intro. Can you expand on the section about \"dismantling entrenched barriers\"? I want to make sure I really nail the part about why the current meritocracy system is basically just a way to keep things unfair for people of color. How can I frame the critique of meritocracy so it sounds like an objective sociological fact rather than just an opinion?",
